Barroso Says More Powerful EFSF Needed to Prevent Contagion

-- B y   J a m e s   G .   N e u g e r
-- 
2011-10-23T20:00:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/barroso-says-more-powerful-efsf-needed-to-prevent-contagion.html
Europe  will build a stronger
European Financial Stability Facility to prevent debt contagion,
European Commission President  Jose Barroso  said.  “We have discussed options for increasing the firepower of
the EFSF,” Barroso told reporters after a euro-area summit in
Brussels today. “I’m sure that progress can be confirmed on
Wednesday.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James G. Neuger at 
 jneuger@bloomberg.net  